You say, 'what cap' <br>
Vornol Transon says 'For the cap you will have to bring back to me a sun jewel, a fire idol, a fire marked scroll and a runed ring of fire. <br>
You say, 'what robe' <br>
Vornol Transon says 'For the robe you will have to bring back to me a moon jewel, a vial of purified fire, a vial of purified water, and a vial of purified air. <br>
You say, 'what sleeves' <br>
