You say, 'I am a magician' <br>
Galdara Swiftwind says 'Very good, the pieces that I have are the sandals, mask, cloak, gloves, choker, belt, and a staff. <br>
You say, 'what sandals' <br>
Galdara Swiftwind says 'For the sandals you must bring me an astral jewel, a talisman of wind, and a mark of aeration. <br>
You say, 'what mask' <br>
Galdara Swiftwind says 'For the mask you must bring me a sun jewel, a talisman of earth, and a sack of shadowed soil. <br>
